### VoiceNova AI — REST Client Tests
### Open in VS Code with "REST Client" extension and click "Send Request"
### Install extension: humao.rest-client

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@sessionId = {{startConversation.response.body.session_id}}

### ─────────────────────────────────────────────
### 0. Health Check
### ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# @name health
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

###

### ─────────────────────────────────────────────
### 1. Check what context / knowledge was loaded
### ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# @name contextCheck
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/test/context-summary

###

### ─────────────────────────────────────────────
### 2. Start a Hindi conversation
### ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# @name startConversation
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/test/conversation
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "language": "hi-IN",
  "caller_number": "+919876543210",
  "purpose": "support"
}

###

### ─────────────────────────────────────────────
### 3. Send Hindi message (auto-detects language)
### ─────────────────────────────────────────────
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/test/message
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "session_id": "PASTE_SESSION_ID_HERE",
  "message": "Mujhe Pro plan ke baare mein jaankari chahiye"
}

###

### ─────────────────────────────────────────────
### 4. Send Tamil message (language switches automatically)
### ─────────────────────────────────────────────
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/test/message
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "session_id": "PASTE_SESSION_ID_HERE",
  "message": "என் கடவுச்சொல்லை மாற்ற வேண்டும்"
}

###

### ─────────────────────────────────────────────
### 5. Send English message
### ─────────────────────────────────────────────
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/test/message
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "session_id": "PASTE_SESSION_ID_HERE",
  "message": "What is your refund policy?"
}

###

### ─────────────────────────────────────────────
### 6. Test language detection standalone
### ─────────────────────────────────────────────
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/test/detect-language
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "ನನಗೆ ಸಹಾಯ ಬೇಕು"
}

###

### ─────────────────────────────────────────────
### 7. End conversation (triggers self-learning)
### ─────────────────────────────────────────────
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/test/end
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "session_id": "PASTE_SESSION_ID_HERE",
  "quality_score": 4.5
}

###

### ─────────────────────────────────────────────
### 8. Add new knowledge via API (no file needed)
### ─────────────────────────────────────────────
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/training/text
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "category": "faq",
  "title": "Shipping Info",
  "content": "We ship within 2 business days. Free shipping above Rs 500. COD available. Track your order at track.mycompany.com",
  "language": "en"
}

###

### ─────────────────────────────────────────────
### 9. Hot-reload knowledge base (after editing files)
### ─────────────────────────────────────────────
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/training/reload

###

### ─────────────────────────────────────────────
### 10. View facts the agent learned from calls
### ─────────────────────────────────────────────
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/training/learned-facts?limit=10

###

### ─────────────────────────────────────────────
### 11. Approve a learned fact
### ─────────────────────────────────────────────
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/training/facts/fact_abc12345
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "approved": true
}

###

### ─────────────────────────────────────────────
### 12. Simulate Twilio inbound call (raw TwiML)
### ─────────────────────────────────────────────
POST {{baseUrl}}/webhooks/twilio/inbound
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

CallSid=TEST_SID_001&From=%2B919876543210&To=%2B911800000000&CallStatus=ringing

###

### ─────────────────────────────────────────────
### 13. Simulate Twilio transcription (caller spoke)
### ─────────────────────────────────────────────
POST {{baseUrl}}/webhooks/twilio/transcription
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

CallSid=TEST_SID_001&SpeechResult=Mujhe+refund+chahiye&Confidence=0.94&LanguageCode=hi-IN

###
